<html>
  <body
    style="margin:0;padding:24px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;line-height:1.5;color:#222;"
  >
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">
      You have been added as a VX Academy Representative for your organisation.
      To get started, please:
    </p>

    <ol style="margin:0 0 16px 20px;padding:0;">
      <li>Set your password</li>
      <li>Complete your profile</li>
      <li>Generate your organisation's unique enrollment URLs</li>
    </ol>

    <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;">
      <a
        href="{{url}}"
        style="display:inline-block;text-decoration:none;background:#d2691e;color:#ffffff;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:6px;font-weight:bold;"
      >
        ðŸ‘‰ Complete Profile &amp; Generate URLs
