    <ul style="margin:0 0 16px 20px;padding:0;">
      <li>Generating and sharing enrollment URLs with your frontliners.</li>
      <li>Ensuring all frontliners register and begin training.</li>
      <li>Acting as the main point of contact for training-related communication
        within your organisation.</li>
      <li>Encouraging participation and monitoring completion rates.</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;">
      Once set up, you'll be ready to invite your frontliners.
    </p>

